•	Pluralsight link for “ Kotlin Fundamentals” https://www.pluralsight.com/courses/kotlin-fundamentals
•	“Kotlin in Action” book by “Dmitry Jemerov and Svetlana Isakova” available here :- https://www.manning.com/books/kotlin-in-action#downloads (chapter 6 and 11 will be free here so that you can download and check the content and then you can buy)
•	Amazon link for “Kotlin in Action” book by “Dmitry Jemerov and Svetlana Isakova” : Buy Kotlin in Action Book Online at Low Prices in India
•	Community-maintained list of links to Kotlin projects, libraries and other resources are available here : - https://kotlinlang.org/docs/resources.html , https://kotlin.link/
•	Kotlin tutorial and books are available in this link https://kotlinlang.org/docs/reference/ , https://kotlinlang.org/docs/books.html
•	Some free video’s and blogs “ 10 KOTLIN TUTORIALS FOR BEGINNERS: DIVE INTO KOTLIN PROGRAMMING [VIDEO COURSE]” link http://petersommerhoff.com/dev/kotlin/kotlin-beginner-tutorial/
